    <!-- AM I PART OF THE PROBLEM -->
    <div class="row">
  	  <div class="col-lg-11 col-lg-offset-1">
  		  <h4 class="text-left">Am I part of the problem? (<a href="https://elizabethsampat.itch.io/am-i-part-of-the-problem" target="_blank">elizabethsampat.itch.io/am-i-part-of-the-problem</a>, Elizabeth Sampat)</h4>
  	  </div>
  	  <div class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-1">
  		  <img src="/img/feminismevent/partoftheproblem.png" class="img-responsive" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
  	  </div>
  	  <div class="col-lg-3">
        <p>Avez-vous blessé quelqu’un? Avez-vous de la difficulté à l’accepter? Êtes-vous dans le doute sur les prochains pas? “Am I Part Of The Problem?” vous guidera à travers vos actions, comment et quand s’excuser, et surtout, comment réparer vos torts.</p>
	  	  <!--p><strong>Avertissement de contenu: </strong></p-->
  	  </div>
  	  <div class="col-lg-3">
        <p>Did you hurt someone? Are you having trouble coming to terms with it? Are you unsure what to do next? Am I Part Of The Problem? will walk you through what you did, how and when to apologize, and most importantly, how to make amends.</p>
